{"id":13629,"date":"2022-07-15T11:32:39","date_gmt":"2022-07-15T04:32:39","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=13629"},"modified":"2022-07-11T11:37:28","modified_gmt":"2022-07-11T04:37:28","slug":"hyundai-dau-tu-16-ty-usd-vao-phat-trien-va-san-xuat-xe-dien","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-dau-tu-16-ty-usd-vao-phat-trien-va-san-xuat-xe-dien\/","title":{"rendered":"Hyundai \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 16 t\u1ef7 USD v\u00e0o ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"article__sapo cms-desc\"><strong>Hyundai mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n v\u00e0 h\u00e3ng \u0111ang chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00f3a \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<\/strong><\/div>\n<div class=\"article__body cms-body \">\n<p>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 r\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p \u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0nh c\u1ea1nh tranh, v\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi xe \u0111i\u1ec7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh xu h\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn. Hyundai c\u0169ng \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng xe \u0111i\u1ec7n trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c n\u00e0y. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u00f4 t\u00f4 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, cha \u0111\u1ebb c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu xe Hyundai Ioniq 5 v\u00e0 Kona Electric \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y khi \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_13472\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13472\" style=\"width: 640px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/danh-gia-xe-dien-hyundai-ioniq-5-tu-trai-nghiem-khach-hang-nhieu-uu-diem-hay-nhieu-khuyet-diem\/hyundai-ioniq-5\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13472\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13472\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/3776129-cham-diem-hyundai-ioniq-5-0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"428\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/3776129-cham-diem-hyundai-ioniq-5-0.jpg 640w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/3776129-cham-diem-hyundai-ioniq-5-0-300x201.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" \/><\/a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-13472\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Hyundai IONIQ 5<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, Hyundai \u0111ang c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 16,5 t\u1ef7 USD \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111i\u1ec7n kh\u00ed h\u00f3a \u0111\u1ed9i xe c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, nh\u1eb1m m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch l\u00e0m cho h\u00e3ng xe n\u00e0y gi\u1ea3m ph\u00e1t th\u1ea3i carbon trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. C\u0169ng c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd r\u1eb1ng, kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia \u0111\u1ec1u trong t\u00e1m n\u0103m.<\/p>\n<p>To\u00e0n b\u1ed9 t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 Kia v\u00e0 h\u00e3ng xe h\u1ea1ng sang Genesis, \u0111ang d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn b\u00e1n 1,4 tri\u1ec7u chi\u1ebfc \u00f4 t\u00f4 \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2030. M\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 16,5 t\u1ef7 USD s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00f3. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1eady, doanh s\u1ed1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch l\u1edbn h\u01a1n, ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3,2 tri\u1ec7u xe \u0111i\u1ec7n tr\u00ean to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u. Hyundai \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh h\u00e3ng s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n trong nh\u1eefng th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 t\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/danh-gia-xe-dien-hyundai-ioniq-5-tu-trai-nghiem-khach-hang-nhieu-uu-diem-hay-nhieu-khuyet-diem\/screenshot-2022-06-10-142001\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13484\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-13484\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Screenshot-2022-06-10-142001.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Screenshot-2022-06-10-142001.jpg 998w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Screenshot-2022-06-10-142001-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Screenshot-2022-06-10-142001-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u xe \u0111i\u1ec7n mang nh\u00e3n hi\u1ec7u Hyundai v\u00e0 Kia. C\u00f4ng ty \u00f4 t\u00f4 Hyundai c\u0169ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 bao g\u1ed3m kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 5,5 t\u1ef7 USD v\u00e0o c\u00e1c c\u01a1 s\u1edf t\u1ea1i Hoa K\u1ef3, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Georgia, hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u h\u1ea1ng sang Rivian. C\u00e1c nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y c\u00f3 tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf t\u1ea1i Hoa K\u1ef3 n\u00e0y d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd s\u1edbm b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t, v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf b\u1edfi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t ngu\u1ed3n cung hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t x\u01b0\u1edfng kho\u1ea3ng 300.000 xe m\u1ed7i n\u0103m.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 v\u1ed1n v\u00e0 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng Hyundai s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u201cg\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3\u201d trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c xe \u0111i\u1ec7n. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng xe \u0111i\u1ec7n ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Hoa K\u1ef3.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/tc-group-hyundai-motor-gioi-thieu-xe-dien-ioniq-5-tai-viet-nam\/10-1\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13316\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-13316\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/10-1-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/10-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/10-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/10-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/10-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/10-1-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?attachment_id=13630\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13630\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13630\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/999981-6892.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"645\" height=\"430\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/999981-6892.jpg 645w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/999981-6892-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 645px) 100vw, 645px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Theo s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a Hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u00f4t\u00f4 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (KAMA), trong qu\u00fd 1 n\u0103m nay, Hyundai v\u00e0 Kia \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t kh\u1ea9u t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 111.252 chi\u1ebfc \u00f4t\u00f4 th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, t\u0103ng 28,6% so v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng k\u1ef3 n\u0103m 2021. \u201cB\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ea3y v\u1ecdt\u201d v\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t kh\u1ea9u c\u1ee7a hai nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u00f4t\u00f4 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1edfi doanh s\u1ed1 b\u00e1n xe ch\u1ea1y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 m\u1eabu xe IONIQ 5 v\u00e0 EV6, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n plug-in hybrid c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c m\u1eabu SUV Santa Fe c\u1ee7a Hyundai v\u00e0 Sorento c\u1ee7a Kia.<\/p>\n<p>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y m\u1eabu xe Hyundai Ioniq 5 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch tham kh\u1ea3o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Kia EV6 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Thaco \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tuy nhi\u00ean th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1eabu xe n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1.<\/p>\n<p>ngu\u1ed3n: <a href=\"http:\/\/tienphong.vn\">tienphong.vn<\/a><\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><strong>HYUNDAI H\u1ea2I PH\u00d2NG<\/strong><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>Hotline kinh doanh: 0906.026.299<\/strong><\/span><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\